metadata.name: FOTObook Two
metadata.description:
This limited edition FOTObook Two features twelve one of one artworks from four world-renowned photographers: J.N. Silva, Alejandro Cartagena, Isaac “Drift” Wright, and Dave Krugman. The pioneering smart contract created by Transient Labs allows this digital book to be completely readable on-chain.

[View Fullscreen](https://timepieces.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/QmR45LjZgaaVo6r8egZRXWXkQVriGz3pyPXZeCL4psiLaQ/FOTO_book_vault_2.html)
